# ── Claude Code ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
/.claude

# graphify knowledge-graph cache — commit the prebuilt graph + content-addressed
# LLM extraction cache (portable: keyed by content-hash + relative path, so a clone
# reuses it instead of paying the token cost to regen). Ignore machine-specific and
# regenerable-offline parts (stat-index leaks $HOME; graph.html rebuilds from cache).
/graphify-out/*
!/graphify-out/graph.json
!/graphify-out/GRAPH_REPORT.md
!/graphify-out/manifest.json
!/graphify-out/cache/
/graphify-out/cache/*
!/graphify-out/cache/ast/
!/graphify-out/cache/semantic/
/graphify-out/cache/stat-index.json

